Title: Competing Predictions
Type: Feature
Units_of_Work: 1000
--
For best prediction quality all the configured prediction engines should be run at all times and compete with each other. The current best predictor would then be given permission to display its predictions. Predictions should be based upon the last hundred characters of user input or so.